                     <interp inst="t17570223-18-person161" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known the prisoner from his birth. I never heard any thing amiss of him in my life.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="175702230011"></xptr>Mr. Winter. The prisoner took a lodging of me about a fortnight after Christmas last; he behaved very honestly, and was very industrious.</p>
