            . I have known him ever since he was born. I always took him to be as sober a person as ever was born. I never heard the least ill word of him in my life.</p>
               <p>Fra. Vaughan. I have known him sixteen years, I never heard any thing amiss of him; he lodged with me about last Michaelmas, and behaved extremely well, he was never out of his lodgings after ten or eleven o'clock.</p>
